latestIgtvVideos.title: My 21st Birthday 🎂
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
With no birthday parties due to social distancing, I had to make the most of my birthday from home. But I’ll be very honest, the best birthday till date. All the emotions combined where in I laugh, I cry, I love and you’ll know. It was a blast... so from the start I’ll explain. 
Usually people cut cakes at 12 and that is what I did. Thinking that is the only thing which can happen throughout my birthday but I was clueless what my family and friends had planned out my entire day. 
Waking up with a  surprised look on my face, I saw my bestfriend @dhrutimehta_ in front me. I thought it was a dream. Later still can’t understand what’s happening I saw @priyashahh_ and @_hetvi_28_  in my kitchen.
I had to decide what brunch menu I would like to go with. Everything was prepared by these cuties I was treated like a queen. The best cottage cheese toast, pancakes ki cake. To be honest, I’m proud and I’m glad. Thank you girlfriends. 

It was evening already, I thought the time is running as I didn’t even take a bath till then, kaise leti? I was busy spending my best birthday. Later I was packed in my room and was not allowed in our children’s room. I thought @thats.krisha and @vanshikashah__ @khushbu_54 @meetshah5454 are cooking something up for my birthday obviously. But I was shocked to see my whole family there. As you can see in the video, my smile says it all.
I couldn’t digest the fact that my day got over so quickly... but wait @thats.krisha and @vanshikashah__ had planned something more too. And I was so eager that I didn’t have my dinner but sat down in my living room seeing what have these guys done for me. @vanshikashah__ amazing video, I never had a thought that you can do something like this for me. You’ve my heart. @krisha you creative bitch. Thank you for everything.
Special thanks to @ziaulhaque @smittshahh and @kkphotole @rajshahhhh
Lastly, my Instagram family. Your birthday wishes made my #birthday more amazing. My friends who called me, who texted me, who video called me. You guys are the reason of me smiling daily.
To the best 21st ever.
Thank you and keep supporting me.
Thankyou @ziaulhaque for making it more amazing by editing It ❤️
#bestbirthdayever

latestPosts.caption:
Hona tha pyaar🌺🌸🌷

“Want to own this dress? Comment below for the link!”

I’m still in awe that we reached 100K followers❤️

It is such a weird feeling, one moment it feels like ‘okay no biggie’ and next moment l’m all ‘oo it’s a big deal’ lol🙈 

I remember the countless nights spent on creating content, and the endless hours spent creating and editing. 

But most of all, I remember the struggles. The self-doubt, the fear of failure, and the moments when I felt like giving up. But I didn’t. And that’s because of all of you🫶🏻

Your love, support, and encouragement have meant the world to me. Thank you for being part of this journey 🥹
 
And I’m grateful for my man for his support and helping me with all my challenges and also for dragging him for my shoots🙈❤️ @manavdoshi 

Beautiful cake by @bakeologymoms 🤍
